{
  "id": "adv_card_ski_10_03",
  "title": "白石沙季 3話 私がもし恋をするとしたら",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hoshiarcade-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hoshiarcade-00-noon",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――ロケ本番中",
      "translations": {
        "en": "—During the filming",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_10_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_10_03-ski001.m4a",
      "text": "このお店の和菓子は若い層にも人気があり\nSNSなどで可愛いと評判になっているようです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "The Japanese sweets from this shop are popular\neven among the youth‚ and they’re praised as cute on social media.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 6.2666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hoshiarcade-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hoshiarcade-00-noon",
      "startTime": 10.3333331903
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_10_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_10_03-ski002.m4a",
      "text": "最近ではバレンタインデーに渡すお菓子としても\n選ばれているとか",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Recently‚ they’ve even been chosen\nas Valentine’s Day gifts.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 13.9666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_10_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_10_03-ski003.m4a",
      "text": "小さな梅をかたどった造形なども可愛らしいですし\n贈り物として選ばれるのも納得ですね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "The small plum-shaped designs are also very charming‚\nso it makes sense they’re picked as gifts.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 20.1333331426,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hoshiarcade-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hoshiarcade-00-noon",
      "startTime": 23.2999996663
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_10_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_10_03-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "（ちゃんと勉強してきたおかげか）\n（スムーズにコーナーを進行出来ているな）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（Thanks to her preparation‚）\n（she’s carrying the segment smoothly.）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 25.4999998093,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hoshiarcade-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hoshiarcade-00-noon",
      "startTime": 28.3333329996
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_10_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_10_03-ski004.m4a",
      "text": "梅と言えば、平安時代の人は物を贈る時\n梅の枝を添えて贈ったりしたそうです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Speaking of plums‚ in the Heian period‚ when giving gifts‚\npeople would often attach a plum branch.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 33.2333331426,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_10_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_10_03-ski005.m4a",
      "text": "それだけではなく、贈り物には和歌を添えるのが\n風流であるとされていたとか",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It was also considered refined to include\na poem along with the gift.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 39.9062853246,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hoshiarcade-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hoshiarcade-00-noon",
      "startTime": 42.566666333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_10_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_10_03-ski006.m4a",
      "text": "万葉集や古今和歌集、百人一首などに恋の歌が\n多いのは、そういう背景があるからかもしれません",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That might explain why collections like the Manyoshu‚ Kokinshu‚ and Hyakunin Isshu\ncontain so many love poems.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 47.0999998093,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_10_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_10_03-ski007.m4a",
      "text": "自分の気持ちを歌に乗せ、相手に伝える\n相手はそれを読み、心にそっとしまい込む",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Putting one’s feelings into a poem and sending it‚\nand the other person reading it and tucking it into their heart…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 55.5333331426,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hoshiarcade-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hoshiarcade-00-noon",
      "startTime": 60.0999996663
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_10_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_10_03-ski008.m4a",
      "text": "そういうシチュエーションの尊さこそが\n昔の恋愛の趣深さの理由だったのかな……と",
      "translations": {
        "en": "The beauty of such moments might be the very reason\nwhy love in the old days felt so profound.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 62.7999998093,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hoshiarcade-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hoshiarcade-00-noon",
      "startTime": 67.466666333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_10_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_10_03-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "（ADさんが沙季へ何かカンペを出したみたいだ）\n（沙季さんも恋をしたことはありますか、か）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（Looks like the AD gave Saki some cue cards.）\n（“Have you ever been in love‚ Saki-san?” huh…）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 71.2999998093,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_10_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_10_03-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "（沙季は恋愛に対してかなり初心だが）\n（どう答えるのだろうか……？）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（Saki’s pretty inexperienced with romance‚ though…）\n（I wonder how she’ll answer…?）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 79.0999998093,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hoshiarcade-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hoshiarcade-00-noon",
      "startTime": 81.2333329996
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_10_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_10_03-ski009.m4a",
      "text": "恥ずかしながら、私に恋愛経験はありません\n恋愛映画や小説で雰囲気をたしなむ程度です",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Embarrassingly‚ I have no experience in love.\nI only enjoy the atmosphere through romance movies or novels.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 87.166666476,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_10_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_10_03-ski010.m4a",
      "text": "ですが、アイドルとして活動させていただく中で\n似たような気持ちになることは多々ありました",
      "translations": {
        "en": "However‚ while working as an idol‚\nI’ve often felt something similar.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 94.8999998093,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hoshiarcade-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hoshiarcade-00-noon",
      "startTime": 98.3333329996
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_10_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_10_03-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "（動揺せずに回答出来ているみたいだ）\n（これなら心配はいらないかもな）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（She seems to be answering without faltering.）\n（If it’s like this‚ I don’t need to worry.）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 101.466666476,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hoshiarcade-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hoshiarcade-00-noon",
      "startTime": 104.0333329996
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_10_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_10_03-ski011.m4a",
      "text": "私はアイドル活動をする上で、ファンの方々の\nことを常に考えるようにしています",
      "translations": {
        "en": "As an idol‚ I always keep\nmy fans in mind.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 107.966666476,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_10_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_10_03-ski012.m4a",
      "text": "どんな時でも、忘れることはありません\n私の心の中には常にファンの方々がいます",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I never forget them‚ no matter the time.\nMy fans are always in my heart.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 114.0855448951,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hoshiarcade-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hoshiarcade-00-noon",
      "startTime": 118.2333329996
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_10_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_10_03-ski013.m4a",
      "text": "私がファンの方に向けたこの想いも\nある意味では恋と呼べるのかもしれないですね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "In a sense‚ the feelings I have for my fans\nmight even be called love.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 121.4333331426,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――その日の夕方",
      "translations": {
        "en": "—That evening",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 125.9333329996,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_onsenlobby-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "onsenlobby-00-noon",
      "startTime": 127.1133269152
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_onsenlobby-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "onsenlobby-00-noon",
      "startTime": 127.1133269152
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_10_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_10_03-ski014.m4a",
      "text": "わぁっ……素敵な旅館ですね……\n本当に今日はここに泊まってもいいんですか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Wow… what a beautiful inn…\nAre you sure we can really stay here tonight?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 132.7333331426,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_10_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_10_03-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "最近忙しくて休む暇もなかったからな\n沙季にゆっくり休める場をプレゼントしたかったんだ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "We’ve been so busy lately‚ no time to rest.\nI wanted to give you the gift of a place to relax‚ Saki.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 140.7333331426,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_onsenlobby-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "onsenlobby-00-noon",
      "startTime": 144.1999955973
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_10_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_10_03-ski015.m4a",
      "text": "なるほど……ふふっ\n素敵なサプライズをありがとうございます",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I see… fufu.\nThank you for the wonderful surprise.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 146.766666476,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_onsenlobby-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "onsenlobby-00-noon",
      "startTime": 149.9999955973
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_10_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_10_03-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "とりあえず、荷物を置いたら自由時間にしよう\n温泉でも散策でも、好きに過ごしてくれていいからな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "For now‚ let’s put down our luggage and then have free time.\nYou can do whatever you like—hot spring or stroll.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 154.0333331426,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――三十分後",
      "translations": {
        "en": "—Thirty minutes later",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 158.7999955973,
      "sfxList": [
