      "text": "今日のロケが成功したのも{user}さんが\n下見に付き合ってくれたおかげですし",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Today’s shoot being a success was also thanks to you‚ {user}-san‚\nfor accompanying me in the location check.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 209.5999967575,
      "sfxList": []
