      "text": "……素直な気持ちを和歌に乗せて贈っていた\n昔の人の気持ちが今なら分かる気がします",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Now I feel like I can understand those people\nwho earnestly conveyed their feelings through poems.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 233.0333178837,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
