      "text": "愛しい人に会うことすら難しかったからこそ\n素を出せる機会を大事にしていたのかもしれません",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Because even meeting their beloved was difficult‚\nthey must have cherished those chances to be genuine.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 240.4999825159,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
